About This Collection

This repository contains high-quality guitar chord audio samples recorded specifically for the ChordCrack ear training application. The samples include:

- Major and minor chord recordings
- Power chord samples
- Barre chord variations
- 7th and extended chord samples
- Individual string recordings for progressive learning

All samples are recorded in high quality and optimized for mobile applications and educational use.

